,Recommended,320670,13976130,"Posted: 13 January, 2015",all,purplepenguinjen,"This third iteration of the series adds an arcade mode. The Story mode is half collapse style puzzles and half other puzzles types including hidden object, sorting picture tiles, find the difference, and some arcade style mini games.  The story is mildly amusing.  My only complaint is the the final piece of the story never shows, so you have no idea how the story ends.  This game is recommended for those who love puzzle games."
